Here is a good article the employees can refer to when researching on Intranets

It highlights how an intranet is a secure internal platform for organizations that enhances communication, collaboration, and information sharing among employees.
It acts as a central hub for resources, improving productivity and engagement while providing easy access to important documents and company policies.



